ML-RSIM/Lamix Release 5/25/2005

Quick Installation:

1. Configure lamix kernel
   cd lamix/arch/lamix_ws/conf/
   config LAMIX_WS

2. Compile lamix
   cd lamix/
   make

3. Compile simulator binary
   cd bin/
   make

4. Cleaning up
   cd bin/
   make clobber
   cd ..
   cd lamix/
   make clean_dist


Directories:
apps/		utilities and sample/test applications
bin/		platform-specific simulator binaries
doc/		documentation
lamix/		Lamix kernel sources, binaries and libraries
sim_mounts/	mount points for simulated file systems
src/		simulator source code
